text:
(15/16) GAME MECHANICS

- Strategy when it comes to minting Obelisk & Land
- Risk & Reward with quests difficulty (Safe, Normal, Degen)
- Loots (Chests, Keys, 2 currencies)
- 4 Bosses (Each drops a different artifact)
- Final Boss (Burn all 4 artifacts to fight)
- Season-based

(14/16) ROADMAP - APPROX. TIMELINE

**Q2**
Mint
Staking
Obelisk & Land
$TROPY Marketplace
Merch
NFT World Con
Season 1 Kickoff

**Q3**
Leaderboard
L2 Bridge
Questing Part 1
Allies collection
Questing Part 2
Final Boss
Season 1 Ends
Prizes

**Q4**
Season 2 Kickoff

text:
(13/16) UTILITY - DAY 1

Here's a list of what you get on Day 1:
- Staking
- Obelisks & Land (2 collections mintable with in-game currency only)
- NFT World Con Event Lifetime Pass (software, recordings, etc.)
- $TROPY Marketplace (WLs, discounts)
- IP Rights
- Top level Art

(12/16) ART

We wanted extremely high-quality art.

It was very important to us that everything would be amazing to look at, even for a P2E game.

We're working with 7 ridiculously talented designers who have worked on Fortnite, Star Wars, EA Games and more.

(11/16) VISION

A simple but in-depth game.

Simple enough so you don't need a PhD to get started.

We want to help the effort onboarding more people in the P2E space.

In-depth enough so all you degens can enjoy the intricacies on a daily basis.

A simple yet very hard thing...

(10/16) PRODUCT

We can have the greatest community, team, vision, funding, whatever...

If we build a literal pile of human excrements for a product, we will fail.

Creating an amazing product will make EVERYTHING else a lot easier!

(9/16) COMMUNITY

We're NOTHING without our community.

We focus on building a core group of loyal fans.

Big numbers are exciting... but are very deceiving.

We will continue to grow as long as we can keep the quality of our community very high.

â¤ï¸ Immortal Army

(8/16) VALUES - ADAPT

The NFT space changes fast.

A roadmap is great but shit will inevitably go wrong or not as expected.

How you react under pressure & correct course is more important.

Strong opinions, weakly held. If there is a better way, we'd be dumb to not adapt.

(7/16) VALUES - LONG & SHORT

While a long-term vision is important, you have to over deliver in the short-term to make it happen.

A long-term vision should NOT be an excuse to do nothing in the short term.

The world is filled with big talkers & little doers ğŸ¤·.

(6/16) VALUES - CUSTOMER EXPERIENCE

People remember how you made them feel... not what you said.

How can we create little moments of joy? Improve their experience?

Go above & beyond?

We believe people can tell who really cares and it makes a big difference in the long run.

(5/16) VALUES - TRANSPARENCY

We don't have all the answers.

We're not perfect.

We over communicate to our community.

We share our struggles, failures & experiences.

We under promise. (My CMO hates me ğŸ¤£)

We can only guarantee one thing - we'll be here working tomorrow...

(4/16) DOXXED TEAM

Two founders with experience building & scaling 9 figure companies.

Previous experience in the gaming space - scaling a gaming peripherals company & e-sport team.

Early experience in other great P2E projects - @EtherOrcs @EthernalElves @dogewoodnft & more.

(3/16) Utility First P2E

A new genre of P2E NFT.

Lead with utility and back it up with the game.

How?
- Hosting our own event (NFT World Con)
- Marketplace driven by our in-game currency
- NFT Analytics Software
- Free & discounted merch
- Community events and more

(2/16) SO... WHAT IS METAVOLUTION?

It's a utility-first P2E on-chain NFT Game on the Ethereum network.

Our whole ecosystem is driven by our currency. All other mints will be with that currency.

We will only succeed by making the project great, not by selling you more shit.

(1/16) OVERVIEW - What it's NOT

We're not building a Metaverse. 

It's a BS promise that projects use. (except @yugalabs & @punk6529)

We're not hosting yatch parties.

We're not giving away $1m.

There's no DAO.

We're not waiting post-mint to see if we "build stuff"...

What makes MetaVolution one of a kind, a Thread ğŸ§µ

It's a new P2E NFT Project by a 9-figure gaming entrepreneur.

In this ğŸ§µ I'll cover...Overview, Team, Values, Vision, Community, Art, Utility, Roadmap, Game Mechanics.
